title: I might've been hacked
body: I had League open and was watching Youtube when I randomly got a Hex Tech Chest. I went and checked why and who got the chest because the last person I played was on free rotation, however when I clicked the most recently played it said I played Udyr last. As you can see here, https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/321488865439514634/344345069207158794/unknown.png But when I checked my match history, Kayn was my last played as seen here, https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/321488865439514634/344344990073225228/unknown.png I honestly don't know what's happening and already changed my password to my account. If anyone can share some light on this it would be very helpful.

replies.body: You did the right thing by changing your password on your account! I didn't see any strange activity, so it may be best to run through our[ Account Protection](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201751664) guide just to take extra precaution.
